 are good too in comparison. Internet is expensive at the hotel.10p a minute. Couldnt find any internet cafe there. Telephone calls too are pricy. Take the train to Xian from there. Flights are overpriced &amp; can be cancelled at will; as ours to Hong Kong was.	
